The following data were obtained during the first order thermal decomposition of a gas A at constant volume :<br/><br/>
$\mathrm{A}(\mathrm{g}) \rightarrow 2 \mathrm{~B}(\mathrm{~g})+\mathrm{C}(\mathrm{g})$ <br/><br/>
